{"tid":1488132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港政府一定比外國勢力滲透左","createTime":"2019-08-19T14:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T14:13:33.000Z","uid":80473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1c1bc1a9c3a2437d9e36ac66da35681353f3cf26","tid":1488132,"uid":80473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:07:45.000Z","msg":"我好痛心<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兩個月尼咁多暴徒係街上面殺人放火丶搞亂香港民生經濟</span></strong></span><br />\n我都要返工揾食架<br />\n而家咁多暴徒搞事<br />\n搞到樓價日日升<br />\n升到我都買唔到樓啊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解政府兩個月尼都冇辦法處理好暴徒嘅問題架</span></strong></span><br />\n警察係咪做唔到野架<br />\n捉晒班暴徒咪冇人出尼搞亂香港囉<br />\n連我都知道出尼搞事有錢收啊<br />\n但係點解警察過左兩個月仲未捉到出錢果班人架<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我交稅比政府去解決問題</span></strong></span><br />\n政府高官月入幾十萬<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但係佢到而家都解決唔到問題</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪比外國勢力滲透左啊</span></strong></span><br />\n點解中央政府唔管下香港政府呢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪連中央政府都比外國勢力滲透左啊</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"58ace45fb67b23a3b791085d2b53131deae89328","tid":1488132,"uid":163447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:13:33.000Z","msg":"習明澤呀,而家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}